### 7. **Related Utilities**

**Lexical helper functions** (`C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_mobile_app\apps\mobile\src\lib\content\lexical.ts`):
- `toLexicalFromPlainText()`: Converts plain text to Lexical JSON structure
- `extractPlainTextFromLexical()`: Extracts text from Lexical tree (walks recursively)
- `stripHtml()`: HTML-to-text conversion

### 8. **Rendering Flow Diagram**

```
LexicalRenderer (main component)
  ↓
  parseContent() → extracts root
  ↓
  root.children.map() → RenderNode() for each
  ↓
  RenderNode (handles blocks)
    → paragraph/heading/quote/list → children.map() → RenderInline()
    → image/link (block) → direct render
    → default → recursive RenderNode()
  ↓
  RenderInline (handles inline)
    → text/linebreak → TextSpan()
    → link (inline) → Text with onPress
    → default → recursive RenderInline()
  ↓
  TextSpan (renders formatted text)
    → applies format flags (bold, italic, underline, strikethrough)
    → returns Text with computed styles
```

This architecture is extensible and modular—adding mention support requires just a new case in both `RenderNode()` and `RenderInline()`, plus a wrapper component to provide navigation context.
